Name: Kao Rune
Description: This rune symbolizes ill intent, lasting suffering, and misfortune. It is commonly known as the rune of curses, allowing those who wield it the ability to inflict calamity upon their foes.
Types: Rune
Rune: While wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECurse of RegretSPACEAs an action, you attempt to curse a target within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you with terrible regret. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be cursed for TIME2-4TIME rounds. For the duration, whenever the target makes an attack against a creature they must take the Help action as a bonus action, helping the creature they targeted. A creature that succeeds on its saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 3 runic attunement slots.
